<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>VAT number</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Only applies to deliveries within the EU.<br>
This setting does not have any effect for non-EU locations.<br>
