<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="500">3.5. Issuing an invoice for export shipments</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>For each accounting location you can individually define whether the invoice for export shipments is net or gross. The basic assumption is that your business is based in the European Union. The setting is applied if the delivery is sent to a country outside the European Union. Your customers receive an invoice without VAT if the invoice is net.</p>
